---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="About Jacob Matlock | Wichita Cash Home Buyer"
  description="Jacob Matlock is a Wichita-area real estate investor and the founder of Pillar Home Buyers. Learn his story and why he started buying houses."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Jacob Matlock</h1>
      <p>Local investor. Wichita native. Straight shooter.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content-page">
      <h2>Who Is Jacob?</h2>
      <p>I grew up in the Derby, Kansas area. Before real estate, I worked as a non-destructive testing technician at a refinery in McPherson — long hours, physical work, and a job that taught me the value of doing things right the first time.</p>
      <p>I started buying houses in March 2023 and went full-time in March 2024. I'm not a guru with a course to sell. I'm just a guy who found a way to help homeowners in tough spots while building something of his own.</p>
      <p>My wife Savannah and I are raising our family here. This is our community. When I buy a house in Wichita, I'm investing in the same place I live — and that matters to me.</p>

      <h2>Why I Started Buying Houses</h2>
      <p>I believed — and still believe — that being a good person will produce a greater ROI than any strategy. That sounds simple, but it's actually a pretty different way to run a real estate business.</p>
      <p>A lot of cash buyers show up with lowball offers and high-pressure tactics. I take the opposite approach: show up honestly, tell you what I think your house is worth, explain my offer, and let you decide. No games.</p>

      <h2>What You Can Expect From Me</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>A real conversation — not a sales pitch</li>
        <li>A fair offer based on actual market data</li>
        <li>Straight answers even if they're not what you want to hear</li>
        <li>A smooth, professional closing with a local title company</li>
        <li>Me picking up my phone when you call</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Let's Talk</h2>
      <p>If you're thinking about selling, give me a call. Even if you're not sure yet — I'm happy to walk through your options with no pressure and no obligation.</p>
      <p><a href="tel:3168162983"><strong>(316) 816-2983</strong></a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <section class="cta-block">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to Talk?</h2>
      <p>No pressure. Just a straight conversation.</p>
      <a href="tel:3168162983" class="btn-dark">Call (316) 816-2983</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
